32#include <core/client.h>

35#include <nvif/class.h>
36#include <nvif/unpack.h>
37
38int
39nv50_sor_power(NV50_DISP_MTHD_V1)
40{
41 struct nvkm_device *device = disp->base.engine.subdev.device;
42 union {
43 struct nv50_disp_sor_pwr_v0 v0;
44 } *args = data;
45 const u32 soff = outp->or * 0x800;
46 u32 stat;
47 int ret;
48
49 nvif_ioctl(object, "disp sor pwr size %d\n", size);
50 if (nvif_unpack(args->v0, 0, 0, false)) {
51 nvif_ioctl(object, "disp sor pwr vers %d state %d\n",
52 args->v0.version, args->v0.state);
53 stat = !!args->v0.state;
54 } else
55 return ret;
56
57
58 nvkm_msec(device, 2000,
59 if (!(nvkm_rd32(device, 0x61c004 + soff) & 0x80000000))
60 break;
61 );
62 nvkm_mask(device, 0x61c004 + soff, 0x80000001, 0x80000000 | stat);
63 nvkm_msec(device, 2000,
64 if (!(nvkm_rd32(device, 0x61c004 + soff) & 0x80000000))
65 break;
66 );
67 nvkm_msec(device, 2000,
68 if (!(nvkm_rd32(device, 0x61c030 + soff) & 0x10000000))
69 break;
70 );
71 return 0;
72}
73
74static const struct nvkm_output_func
75nv50_sor_output_func = {
76};
77
78int
79nv50_sor_output_new(struct nvkm_disp *disp, int index,
80 struct dcb_output *dcbE, struct nvkm_output **poutp)
81{
82 return nvkm_output_new_(&nv50_sor_output_func, disp,
83 index, dcbE, poutp);
84}
